sentences: Konstanze Eickhorst (born 1961, in Bremen) is a German pianist.
Eickhorst won the IX Clara Haskil (1981) and IV Géza Anda (1988) competitions.
A member of the Linos Ensemble, she has been active at an international level as a soloist and a chamber musician, and has recorded for CPO.
She teaches at the Musikhochschule Lübeck.
